x1 <- c(1, 1.5, 1.5, 4,2)
x2 <- c(1000, 1100, 2000, 1000, 1250) 
set.seed(2708)
y <- rbinom(n = length(x2), size = 2,prob = 0.6)
simpledata = data.frame(x1,x2,y)
library(ggplot2)
ggplot(simpledata, aes(x=x1, y=x2, color=factor(y)))+

plotknn <- function (knnregname){
  ggplot()+
  geom_point(data = simpledata, aes(x=x,y=y, size = 2.5, color = "green", alpha = 0.6))+
  geom_step(aes(x=testrange$test_range, y = knnregname$pred, color = "red"))+
  theme(legend.position = "none")  
}
plotknn(knnReg1)

set.seed(42)
idx <- sample(1:nrow(Boston), size = 250)
trn_boston <- Boston[idx, ]
tst_boston <- Boston[-idx, ]
RMSEtrain <- NULL
RMSEtest <- NULL

for (i in 1:50){
  trainknn <- knn.reg(train = trn_boston[, -1],  
                      test = trn_boston[,-1], y = trn_boston$crim, k = i)
  testknn <- knn.reg(train = trn_boston[, -1],  test = tst_boston[,-1], 
                     y = trn_boston$crim, k = i)
  RMSEtrain[i] <- sqrt(mean((trn_boston$crim - trainknn$pred)^2))
  RMSEtest[i] <- sqrt(mean((tst_boston$crim - testknn$pred)^2))
}
df <- data.frame(x = 1:50, train = RMSEtrain, test = RMSEtest)
ggplot(data = df, aes(x = x, y = train)) +
  geom_point(color = "blue")+
  labs(y = "Train RMSE", x = "k", title="Train RMSE")

ggplot(data = df, aes(x = x, y = test))+
  geom_point(color="blue")+ geom_line()+
  labs(y = "Test RMSE", x = "k", title="Test RMSE")

plotknn(knnReg1) + geom_smooth( aes(x=x, y=y), method = "lm", se = F)

library(ggvoronoi)
## Warning: package 'ggvoronoi' was built under R version 3.5.3
set.seed(45056)
x <- sample(1:200,100)
y <- sample(1:200,100)
z <- rbinom(n = 100, size = 1, prob = 0.6)
length(z)
## [1] 100
ggplot(data.frame(x,y,z),aes(x,y, col=factor(z))) +
  stat_voronoi(geom="path") +
  geom_point()+theme(legend.position = "none")  

points <- data.frame(x, y,
                     distance = sqrt((x-100)^2 + (y-100)^2))
circle <- data.frame(x = 100*(1+cos(seq(0, 2*pi, length.out = 2500))),
                     y = 100*(1+sin(seq(0, 2*pi, length.out = 2500))),
                     group = rep(1,2500))
ggplot(points) +
  geom_voronoi(aes(x,y,fill=distance))

ggplot(points) +
  geom_point(aes(x,y,color=distance)) +
  geom_path(data=circle,aes(x,y,group=group))

ggplot(points,aes(x,y)) +
  stat_voronoi(geom="path") +
  geom_point()

ggplot(points,aes(x,y)) +
  geom_voronoi(aes(fill=distance),outline=circle,
               color="#4dffb8",size=.125) +
  scale_fill_gradient(low="#4dffb8",high="black",guide=F) +
  theme_void() +
  coord_fixed()
